snippet.textDisplay:
I have known Jabbar from Nazir Ahmad Music Society of GCU, and he is amazing, he topped there and certainly blow a great whip here, amazing job. However Nirmal performances in morning show "Aik New Subh with Farah", brought her limelight. She is the second youngest artist to perform on CS, first is going to be Daima at 17. It's hard to believe she is just 20 and depth of her voice is marvelous. Good Composition as well.

Score: Roy, 8.81/10, Jabbar 9/10, Over all, 9.2/10
